column5: If you left this behind at a fishing location and can tell me location and model, I have it. It is not a cheap paddle from looking it up on line.  Cheers   Oh,fresh salmon for the smoker Tuesday.
Now that you mention it,I should of went to the truck and brought it in to use on a certain fella. I,ll bet a good swift swing to his arse would of stung good. LMAO
